Afro-pop singer Oluwatobiloba Daniel Anidugbu aka Kizz Daniel has wished his fans “happy new month.” The father of two, who recently welcomed twin sons, took to social media to share a loving video of himself rocking his infants while they appeared to be fast asleep. The video which is void of sound showed Fly Boy Inc boss as he lovingly embraced the little cuties while he rocked them moving from place to place. “ʜᴀᴘᴘʏ ɴᴇᴡ ᴍᴏɴᴛʜ Fʀᴏᴍ ᴅ’ɢʀᴇᴀᴛ.” Fans and colleagues have taken to the comment section to wish the new daddy a “happy new month” too as they also admire the picture-perfect video and prayed for such blessing to visit them. 